<TITLE>Description
</TITLE>
<PARA>
<FUNCTION>__sigpause</FUNCTION> has the same behavior as 
<FUNCTION>sigpause</FUNCTION> as specified by <EMPHASIS>X/Open</EMPHASIS>.
</PARA>
<PARA>
<FUNCTION>__sigpause</FUNCTION> is not in the source standard; 
it is only in the binary standard.
</PARA>
